						               													<description>2020: The Best Year Ever (The Game) is a &amp;ldquo;2020 themed&amp;rdquo; board game. It cleverly uses the events of 2020 to draw players together based on their common experience of the year. &amp;ldquo;Play cards&amp;rdquo; encourage players to &amp;ldquo;act out&amp;rdquo;  common (and their own) 2020 experiences while &amp;ldquo;Point cards&amp;rdquo; memorialize well known AND little known events of 2020 while helping OR hurting a player&amp;rsquo;s &amp;ldquo;score.&amp;rdquo; Using unconventional (and fluid) game rules, players are kept involved and &amp;ldquo;off balance&amp;rdquo; (much like we all were during 2020) as each game unfolds differently depending on the cards drawn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2020: The Best Year Ever (The Game) uses dice, a spinner, and unique cards hat guide players through 2020 related challenges, activities and conversations while players collect (plus and minus) points until the games ends - at any moment - in one of several possible ways. The player with the highest points at the end wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
